{"data":{"markdownRemark":null,"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-plugin-ipfs","description":"Adds support for deploying Gatsby to IPFS by ensuring that assets are relative","keywords":["gatsby","gatsby-plugin","ipfs","ipns","relative"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"satazor","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/da221b94a69db0390abab4c6d75496f6"},"repository":{"url":"https://github.com/moxystudio/gatsby-plugin-ipfs"},"readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-plugin-ipfs\"><a href=\"#gatsby-plugin-ipfs\" aria-label=\"gatsby plugin ipfs permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-plugin-ipfs</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://npmjs.org/package/gatsby-plugin-ipfs\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/npm/v/gatsby-plugin-ipfs.svg\" alt=\"NPM version\"></a> <a href=\"https://npmjs.org/package/gatsby-plugin-ipfs\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/npm/dm/gatsby-plugin-ipfs.svg\" alt=\"Downloads\"></a> <a href=\"https://david-dm.org/moxystudio/gatsby-plugin-ipfs\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/david/moxystudio/gatsby-plugin-ipfs.svg\" alt=\"Dependency status\"></a> <a href=\"https://david-dm.org/moxystudio/gatsby-plugin-ipfs?type=dev\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/david/dev/moxystudio/gatsby-plugin-ipfs.svg\" alt=\"Dev Dependency status\"></a> <a href=\"https://greenkeeper.io\"><img src=\"https://badges.greenkeeper.io/moxystudio/gatsby-plugin-ipfs.svg\" alt=\"Greenkeeper badge\"></a></p>\n<p>Adds support for deploying <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/\">Gatsby</a> websites to <a href=\"https://ipfs.io/\">IPFS</a> by ensuring that assets are relative.</p>\n<h2 id=\"installation\"><a href=\"#installation\" aria-label=\"installation permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Installation</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">$ npm install --save gatsby-plugin-ipfs</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"usage\"><a href=\"#usage\" aria-label=\"usage permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Usage</h2>\n<p>Set <code class=\"language-text\">prefixPath</code> to <code class=\"language-text\">__GATSBY_IPFS_PATH_PREFIX__</code> and include the plugin in your <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code> file:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    pathPrefix<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'__GATSBY_IPFS_PATH_PREFIX__'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">'gatsby-plugin-ipfs'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>And now, simply build the project with <code class=\"language-text\">npm run build -- --prefix-paths</code>. Better yet, set it by default in your <code class=\"language-text\">package.json</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token property\">\"scripts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"build\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"gatsby build --prefix-paths\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"but-how\"><a href=\"#but-how\" aria-label=\"but how permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>But how?</h2>\n<p>It turns out the Gatsby doesn’t support relative paths. But I didn’t gave up and came up with smart and ugly hacks to do so:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Adds a post-build step that iterates over files and transforms every <code class=\"language-text\">__GATSBY_IPFS_PATH_PREFIX__</code> occurrence</li>\n<li>Adds a very small code snippet to every HTML page that defines the <code class=\"language-text\">__GATSBY_IPFS_PATH_PREFIX__</code> global based on the browser location</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"license\"><a href=\"#license\" aria-label=\"license permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>License</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://opensource.org/licenses/MIT\">MIT License</a></p>","timeToRead":1}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-plugin-ipfs/","id":"9218e8e2-15d8-5447-8678-8d74ac122955","layout":"plugins"}}